            },
            "answer_text": "No. The watch will happily carry on telling time and running some applications without the phone. I, for instance, like to go on a run without carrying my phone. So I leave it at home. With just the Apple Watch and AirPods, I can listen to a podcast, while my Nike Running Club App, uses GPS to track my run. But other apps on the watch, will not function without the phone being present. ",
